      • getAllVariablesBound

        public boolean getAllVariablesBound()
        Returns whether all Variables in the clause appear at least once in a positive literal with a StandardPredicate.

        If all Variables are bound, then DatabaseQueries can identify all groundings of the clause with possibly non-zero truth values in a Database.

        Returns:
        whether all Variables are bound
